---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Assembly" description="Flat box to fully assembled in under 3 minutes a cabinet. A full set in less than 1 hour. The only tool you'll need is a screwdriver for the back panel.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="section-container text-center">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto reveal">
        <p class="text-klovo-amber font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
          Fast Assembly
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6 leading-tight">
          Flat box to fully assembled.<br/>In minutes, not a weekend.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-klovo-grey leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          No cam locks. No Allen wrenches. Panels interlock and create a secure construction. A single cabinet assembles in about 2-3 minutes. A full set in less than 1 hour. The only tool you'll need is a screwdriver for the back panel.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Video Section -->
  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto reveal">
        <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden aspect-video bg-charcoal shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="/images/assembly/hands-pressing.png"
            alt="Klovo cabinet assembly demonstration"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80"
            loading="eager"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <button class="w-24 h-24 bg-klovo-blue/90 hover:bg-klovo-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110 shadow-2xl" aria-label="Play assembly video">
              <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
                <polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19" />
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3 Steps -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-warm-neutral">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">Three steps. That's it.</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-klovo-grey max-w-xl mx-auto">A cabinet box in 2-3 minutes. A full set in less than 1 hour.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="text-center reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-klovo-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <span class="text-pure-white font-bold text-xl" style="font-family: var(--font-accent)">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">Unbox the panels</h3>
          <p class="text-klovo-grey leading-relaxed">
            Open the box and lay out the pre-drilled panels.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="text-center reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-klovo-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <span class="text-pure-white font-bold text-xl" style="font-family: var(--font-accent)">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">Push and lock</h3>
          <p class="text-klovo-grey leading-relaxed">
            Align the panels and push them together. The Klovo connector system locks them into a secure, weight-bearing construction. Then drive a few screws through the back panel runners to secure it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="text-center reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-klovo-amber rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <span class="text-charcoal font-bold text-xl" style="font-family: var(--font-accent)">&#10003;</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">Done. Load it up.</h3>
          <p class="text-klovo-grey leading-relaxed">
            That's it. Your cabinet holds 500 lbs and the box took less than a minute to build. All hardware for doors and drawers is easy install too.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Connector -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-warm-neutral aspect-square">
            <img
              src="/images/assembly/hands-garage.png"
              alt="Close-up of the Klovo connector system — panels pressing together"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <p class="text-klovo-amber font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
            The Connector
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6 leading-tight">
            Panels interlock. A secure construction. No tools for the box.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Most cabinet brands use cam locks, dowels, or screws that require tools and patience. Our unique connector system is different: panels push together and lock into a secure, weight-bearing construction.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The only tool you'll need is a screwdriver to secure the back panel through the runners. That's it.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klovo-amber flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
              Panels interlock into a secure construction — no tools for the box itself
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klovo-amber flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
              Easy install hardware with push-to-open hinges and glides
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klovo-amber flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
              Disassembles just as easily (moves with you)
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-warm-neutral">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">Klovo vs. the old way.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto reveal">
        <div class="bg-pure-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full min-w-[480px]">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-warm-neutral">
                <th class="py-4 px-6 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-klovo-grey uppercase tracking-wider"></th>
                <th class="py-4 px-6 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-klovo-blue uppercase tracking-wider">Klovo</th>
                <th class="py-4 px-6 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-klovo-grey uppercase tracking-wider">Traditional</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-warm-neutral/50">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-charcoal">Assembly Time</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-klovo-blue">2-3 min per box, &lt; 1 hour per set</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-center text-klovo-grey">4+ hours</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-warm-neutral/50">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-charcoal">Tools Required</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-klovo-blue">Screwdriver only</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-center text-klovo-grey">Drill, level, hardware</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-warm-neutral/50">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-charcoal">Handles</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-klovo-blue">Push-to-open (none needed)</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-center text-klovo-grey">Hardware required</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-charcoal">Portable</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-center font-semibold text-klovo-blue">Yes, disassembles</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 text-center text-klovo-grey">Permanent</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="section-container text-center reveal">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">Ready to see a set?</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/sets/" class="btn-amber">View Sets <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
        <a href="/where-to-buy/" class="btn-secondary">Find a Retailer</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
